      "content": "hey, im in rio right now and i think i messed up. been out in the sun all day and i feel really weird. im kinda confused and im having a hard time finding the right words when i talk... like i know what i want to say but it isnt coming out right. is this just dehydration or something? i feel super lightheaded.",
